"66cccd4d52a01c89630f71d478e61ac8da01d7e6","tid":1770962,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9013bec10131458a932e09c7a6ffe4be05ab8168","tid":1770962,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:17:08.000Z","msg":"法國總統真係一件奶共撚樣黎　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yxwdhmX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyxwdhmX.png&h=d5ed18ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【北約腦死亡】<br />\n法國馬克龍：中國俄羅斯非敵人 自己不會道歉</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）早前批評北約（NATO）缺乏協調，正處於「腦死亡」狀態，北約成員國的領導人紛紛批評馬克龍言論過激，馬克龍最新表示，他不會為此道歉，北約現在的關鍵問題應該是決定誰是共同敵人。<strong><ins>他指出，北約的敵人是恐怖主義，並非中國或俄羅斯。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n法國馬克龍批北約「腦死亡」德國默克爾：言論過激<br />\n<br />\n法國總統馬克龍（Emmanuel Macron）周四（28日）稱，鑑於蘇聯早已垮台，北約現在的關鍵問題應該是確定誰是共同敵人。「誰是我們共同的敵人？這個問題值得澄清。」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歐洲「恐從地緣上消失」 <strong><ins>馬<br />\n克龍：我們要覺醒不靠美國</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n北約在冷戰後大舉向俄羅斯國境推進，美國國務卿蓬佩奧近日更要求北約劍指中國，但馬克龍表示，北約共同敵人應是恐怖主義，並非中國或俄羅斯：<br />\n<br />\n我們今天的敵人是俄羅斯嗎？是中國嗎？他們是北約的指定敵人嗎？我不這麼認為。聯盟的共同敵人應是恐怖主義，因為它襲擊過我們所有的國家。<br />\n（Is our enemy today， as I hear sometimes， Russia？ Is it China？ Is it the Atlantic alliance's purpose to designate them as enemies？ I don&rsquo;t think so. Our common enemy at the alliance is， it seems， terrorism， which has hit all of our countries.）<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍就某些歐洲國家在軍費上貢獻不足發表言論，他稱：「參與國僅宣稱自己對集體安全的承諾是不夠的。參與國需要證明，一個真正的軍事聯盟意味著行動、決定，而不是空口說白話。」<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍補充，北約成員國之間肯定存在分歧已經不是什麼秘密，但是北約的優勢在於，過去每一次都能夠克服分歧。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"Fuck him"},{"pid":"64a9b9783b2a77e1e75dd9415430d11c98690b9e","tid":1770962,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrwkGRT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrwkGRT.jpg&h=06f56243&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20fa78e509676d5bf1caeed31cb3c2cdf5d6a3f6","tid":1770962,"uid":164608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:31:27.000Z","msg":"香港人有佢哋一半就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a3a18a2e7b1bfdb1b4cb973d8c20032a55e320","tid":1770962,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"馬克龍會唔會係中共暗中捧上去既傀儡總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b65538f85960a4870d0e0aad10b10f3824fccb","tid":1770962,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e04e9059306c034c2a0abc7377a985678bff1b5","tid":1770962,"uid":243366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"香港幾時可以咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"香港: 阻人返工仆街死！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68442268626c336742ba5fd9a3a68b98246d409f","tid":1770962,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"#standwithfrance"},{"pid":"83c5c91db5257a6e2f540ec8908d2253cb7a693f","tid":1770962,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">據早前一項民調顯示，今次全國大罷工獲得法國近七成民眾支持。</code></pre><br />\n屌 點解人地可以話罷就罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02903bac85decfe23b7f7af61214b8b16af03a78","tid":17709